creator: Tabby
descriptionHtml:
TABBY | BUY NOW PAY LATER
With tabby, you can enjoy stress-free shopping at any of our partner stores and make payments over time — with no interest and no fees.
Buy what you want today, get it today and split your purchase into equal monthly installments or simply pay for your purchase 2 weeks later.
USE THE TABBY APP TO:
• See all your current and past tabby orders in one place
• Track payment dates and deadlines
• Easily make payments directly from the app
ABOUT TABBY
We’re here to help you say yes to more of the things you love: online and in-store, with more than 150 partner stores and many more joining every week.
Want it. Buy it. Pay later

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
* Previously, our Shop Directory was only available on our website, now we made your tabby experience much more convenient with having the shop directory on the app featuring new shops you have been waiting for.
* We are not crazy about push notifications either, so we added for you the fun kind only, to keep you up to date with our latest stores launches, and general updates.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What’s new?
- We took shopping to the next level – introducing tabby Cashback. Now you can shop now, pay later and earn cash.
- Shop at your favourite brands with tabby and earn cash. That’s real money, not another loyalty program. You can earn cash regardless of the way you pay.
- Never miss another deal with hundreds of new offers and discounts updated weekly from the region’s top brands.

title: Tabby

creator: Tabby
descriptionHtml:
tabby makes shopping more rewarding by empowering you with the flexibility and freedom to get what you want. With the tabby app, you can shop now and pay later – with no interest, fees or hidden costs of any kind.

How does tabby work?

- Find and visit your favourite stores on the tabby app
- Add what you want to your cart and choose tabby at checkout
- Get approved instantly and link any card
- Split your purchase into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly

SHOP YOUR FAVOURITE BRANDS.

Find your favourites or discover new brands that let you get the most out of shopping. Shop with brands like Adidas, IKEA, 6th Street, Centrepoint, Golden Scent and hundreds more.

SHOP NOW. PAY LATER.

You can split your purchases into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly. So you can get what you love now and make your payments more manageable over time.

GET THE BEST SHOPPING DEALS.

In the tabby app, you'll never miss another a deal with weekly updates and discounts from our retailers.

MANAGE YOUR PAYMENTS.

Track all your shopping in one place – see upcoming bills, change payment methods and get alerts for your next payment.

Follow us to stay up-to-date on new stores and latest deals:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tabbypay/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/paywithtabby/

Need help? Reach out to help.tabby.ai

title: tabby | Shop now. Pay later‪.‬

creator: Tabby
descriptionHtml:
With the Tabby app, you can shop at your favourite brands and split your purchases in 4 interest-free payments – with no interest or hidden fees of any kind. Plus, earn cashback when you shop and access the best deals.

How does Tabby work?

- Find your favourite stores on the Tabby app, where you can see which brands let you split payments in 4 and earn cashback.
- Add what you want to your cart and choose your favourite way to pay.
- Tabby lets you split your purchase into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly.
- You'll earn cashback at select stores that you can withdraw. That's real money, not another loyalty program.

SHOP YOUR FAVOURITE BRANDS.

Find your favourites or discover new brands that let you get the most out of shopping. Shop with brands like SHEIN, Adidas, IKEA, Sivvi, Centrepoint, Golden Scent and thousands more.

SHOP NOW. PAY LATER.

You can split your purchases into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly. So you can get what you love now and make your payments more manageable over time.

GET CASH FOR SHOPPING.

Sign up to Tabby and earn cashback at hundreds of your favourite brands. That's real money you can withdraw, not another loyalty program.

GET THE BEST DEALS.

In the Tabby app, you'll never miss another a deal with daily coupon code drops and discounts from Tabby stores.

MANAGE YOUR PAYMENTS.

Track all your purchases, see upcoming bills, change payment methods and get alerts for your next payment – all in one place.

Tabby creates financial freedom in the way you shop, earn and save by reshaping your relationship with money. A relationship that lets you make the most out of it. One that’s empowering, fair and even playful. Tabby lets you shop now, pay later and earn cash – without the interest, fees or debt traps.

Follow us to stay up-to-date on new stores and latest deals:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tabbypay/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/paywithtabby/

Need help? Reach out to http://help.tabby.ai/

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Two years ago we set out to create financial freedom in the way you shop, earn and save by reshaping your relationship with money. Today we’re unveiling our new brand, where Tabby embodies a new kind of money. One that lets you make the the most out of it. One that’s empowering, fair and even playful.
What's new:
◉ We made improvements under the hood and oiled up our payments engine so your shopping cart rides smooth.
◉ You can now make payments with Apple Pay in the UAE

title: tabby | Shop now. Pay later‪.‬

creator: Tabby
descriptionHtml:
With the Tabby app, you can shop at your favourite brands and split your purchases in 4 interest-free payments – with no interest or hidden fees of any kind. Plus, earn cashback when you shop and access the best deals.

How does Tabby work?

- Find your favourite stores on the Tabby app, where you can see which brands let you split payments in 4 and earn cashback.
- Add what you want to your cart and choose your favourite way to pay.
- Tabby lets you split your purchase into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly.
- You'll earn cashback at select stores that you can withdraw. That's real money, not another loyalty program.

SHOP YOUR FAVOURITE BRANDS.

Find your favourites or discover new brands that let you get the most out of shopping. Shop with brands like SHEIN, Adidas, IKEA, Sivvi, Centrepoint, Golden Scent and thousands more.

SHOP NOW. PAY LATER.

You can split your purchases into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly. So you can get what you love now and make your payments more manageable over time.

GET CASH FOR SHOPPING.

Sign up to Tabby and earn cashback at hundreds of your favourite brands. That's real money you can withdraw, not another loyalty program.

GET THE BEST DEALS.

In the Tabby app, you'll never miss another a deal with daily coupon code drops and discounts from Tabby stores.

MANAGE YOUR PAYMENTS.

Track all your purchases, see upcoming bills, change payment methods and get alerts for your next payment – all in one place.

Tabby creates financial freedom in the way you shop, earn and save by reshaping your relationship with money. A relationship that lets you make the most out of it. One that’s empowering, fair and even playful. Tabby lets you shop now, pay later and earn cash – without the interest, fees or debt traps.

Follow us to stay up-to-date on new stores and latest deals:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tabbypay/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/paywithtabby/

Need help? Reach out to http://help.tabby.ai/

descriptionHtml:
With the Tabby app, you can shop at your favourite brands and split your purchases in 4 interest-free payments – with no interest or hidden fees of any kind. Plus, earn cashback when you shop and access the best deals.

How does Tabby work?

- Find your favourite stores on the Tabby app, where you can see which brands let you split payments in 4 and earn cashback.
- Add what you want to your cart and choose your favourite way to pay.
- Tabby lets you split your purchase into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly.
- You'll earn cashback at select stores that you can withdraw. That's real money, not another loyalty program.

SHOP YOUR FAVOURITE BRANDS.

Find your favourites or discover new brands that let you get the most out of shopping. Shop with brands like SHEIN, Adidas, IKEA, Sivvi, Centrepoint, Golden Scent and thousands more.

SHOP NOW. PAY LATER.

You can split your purchases into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly. So you can get what you love now and make your payments more manageable over time.

GET CASH FOR SHOPPING.

Sign up to Tabby and earn cashback at hundreds of your favourite brands. That's real money you can withdraw, not another loyalty program.

GET THE BEST DEALS.

In the Tabby app, you'll never miss another a deal with daily coupon code drops and discounts from Tabby stores.

MANAGE YOUR PAYMENTS.

Track all your purchases, see upcoming bills, change payment methods and get alerts for your next payment – all in one place.

Tabby creates financial freedom in the way you shop, earn and save by reshaping your relationship with money. A relationship that lets you make the most out of it. One that’s empowering, fair and even playful. Tabby lets you shop now, pay later and earn cash – without the interest, fees or debt traps.

descriptionHtml:
With the Tabby app, you can shop at your favourite brands and split your purchases in 4 interest-free payments – with no interest or hidden fees of any kind. Plus, earn cashback when you shop and access the best deals.

How does Tabby work?

- Find your favourite stores on the Tabby app, where you can see which brands let you split payments in 4 and earn cashback.
- Add what you want to your cart and choose your favourite way to pay.
- Tabby lets you split your purchase into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly.
- You'll earn cashback at select stores that you can withdraw. That's real money, not another loyalty program.

SHOP YOUR FAVOURITE BRANDS.

Find your favourites or discover new brands that let you get the most out of shopping. Shop with brands like SHEIN, Adidas, IKEA, Sivvi, Centrepoint, Golden Scent and thousands more.

SHOP NOW. PAY LATER.

You can split your purchases into 4 interest-free payments, billed monthly. So you can get what you love now and make your payments more manageable over time.

GET CASH FOR SHOPPING.

Sign up to Tabby and earn cashback at hundreds of your favourite brands. That's real money you can withdraw, not another loyalty program.

GET THE BEST DEALS.

In the Tabby app, you'll never miss another a deal with daily coupon code drops and discounts from Tabby stores.

MANAGE YOUR PAYMENTS.

Track all your purchases, see upcoming bills, change payment methods and get alerts for your next payment – all in one place.

Tabby creates financial freedom in the way you shop, earn and save by reshaping your relationship with money. A relationship that lets you make the most out of it. One that’s empowering, fair and even playful. Tabby lets you shop now, pay later and earn cash – without the interest, fees or debt traps.

descriptionHtml:
SHOP NOW. PAY LATER
Tabby lets you shop what you love and split purchases into four monthly payments — with no interest, no hidden fees and no surprises. Whether you're shopping online or in store, Tabby gives you control, financial flexibility and peace of mind.

SHOP FROM TOP BRANDS
Discover and shop your favorite brands including AMAZON, SHEIN, IKEA, ADIDAS, SIVVI, CENTREPOINT, and many more in one shopping app. The Tabby app is your one-stop shopping destination, packed with fashion, electronics, home goods, makeup, and more.

COMPARE PRICES & SAVE MONEY
Track price drops and compare products across multiple stores. With smart alerts, you’ll always get the best deal — your personal price-checker, built right in.

NEW DEALS AND DISCOUNTS EVERY DAY
Shop daily discounts, coupons and promotions from top brands. Never miss a deal — just open the app and see what’s new.

FIND NEARBY STORES THAT ACCEPT TABBY
Use our in-store map to discover shops and malls that accept Tabby. Try before you buy and still pay later. Search by brand, category or location.

ONE APP FOR ALL YOUR SHOPPING
Manage payments, track purchases, get reminders and explore new brands — all in one app.

PROTECT YOUR PURCHASE WITH TABBY CARE
Tabby Care adds extra peace of mind. It covers your purchases, makes returns easy and protects your order every step of the way.

24/7 CUSTOMER SERVICE
Use chat in the Tabby app for round-the-clock support.

Tabby gives you the freedom to pay later with no interest, no fees and no surprises — so you can shop on your terms.
